{
  "texts": [
    "This systematic review conducted a comprehensive search of literature across several databases, including ERIC, Education Source, APA Psychological Information, Web of Science, Engineering Village, ProQuest, Science Direct, and Google Scholar (Fagard et al. 1996; Moher et al. 2009; Pigott and Polanin, 2020).",
    "Moreover, we sourced Chinese papers through search engines such as CNKI and other Chinese search engines (Baidu et al.",
    "Pub Scholar CN) (Goyal, 2020; Meats et al. 2007; Zhang and Cheung, 2003).",
    "This research focused on professional development (PD) and teacher development in STEM projects.",
    "We utilized a combination of thesaurus terms and keywords, specifically targeting titles and abstracts, to ensure the inclusion of all pertinent citations (Ghazi-Mirsaeid and Masoudi, 2017; Goldman and Schmalz, 2004; Rees-Potter, 1989)."
  ]
}